OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will chair Cabinet on
OL,7,FTuesday morning, where the conflict
OL,8,Fand its fallout are likely to feature
OL,9,Fhigh on the agenda.
OL,11,FHe has refused to back the operation
OL,12,Fand was instead working with French
OL,13,FPresident Emmanuel Macron to bring
OL,14,Ftogether an international coalition
OL,15,Faimed at securing future freedom of
OL,16,Fnavigation in the strait, a vital
OL,17,Froute for global oil and gas supplies
OL,18,Ffrom the Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
