OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister told MPs the summit
OL,7,Fof world leaders later this week would
OL,8,Ffocus on diplomatic efforts to reach a
OL,9,F"negotiated end to the conflict" and
OL,10,Fthe reopening of the critical
OL,11,Fwaterway, which had become a "running
OL,12,Fsore" to the world.
OL,14,FMilitary planning would also be
OL,15,Fundertaken "to provide assurance to
OL,16,Fshipping as soon as a stable
OL,17,Fenvironment can be established".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@`O]sD@^OUtD@EO]wD@LOUyD@_O]
