OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776125001
OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,FSir Keir said: "I'm very concerned
OL,7,Fabout the impact that this war is
OL,8,Fhaving on people back in the United
OL,9,FKingdom who've obviously played no
OL,10,Fpart in the war, but I don't want them
OL,11,Fpaying the price.
OL,13,F"So that's my primary focus."
OL,15,FHis comments were echoed by the
OL,16,FChancellor, who said: "Families and
OL,17,Fbusinesses across Britain are bearing
OL,18,Fthe cost of instability they did not
OL,19,Fcause. These are not costs I wanted,
OL,20,Fbut they are costs we will have to
OL,21,Frespond to.
OL,26,@nD@POUuD@AOUuD@]O]xD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
