OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,F"The Iran conflict must be a line in
OL,7,Fthe sand on how we deal with global
OL,8,Fcrisis and instability.
OL,10,F"I will go to America with a clear
OL,11,Fmessage: global leaders must take co-
OL,12,Fordinated economic action and
OL,13,Fsupercharge the path to energy
OL,14,Fsecurity to protect ourselves in the
OL,15,Ffuture."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@HO]
