OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,FSeparately, Deputy Prime Minister
OL,7,FDavid Lammy met with US vice president
OL,8,FJD Vance and secretary of state Marco
OL,9,FRubio in Washington DC where they
OL,10,Fdiscussed the current crisis in the
OL,11,Fstrait.
OL,13,FAmid a fragile ceasefire, Mr Lammy is
OL,14,Funderstood to have highlighted the
OL,15,Frole the UK is playing in the
OL,16,Finternational effort to ensure
OL,17,Fshipping can pass freely through the
OL,18,Fmaritime pinchpoint.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
