OL,3,CFamilies bearing cost of instability,
OL,4,Csays Chancellor amid US Iran blockade
OL,6,FMeanwhile, defending his actions, Mr
OL,7,FTrump said: "We can't let a country
OL,8,Fblackmail or extort the world because
OL,9,Fthat's what they're doing."
OL,11,FHowever, he insisted Iran wants to
OL,12,Fstrike an agreement but did not give
OL,13,Ffurther details.
OL,15,FSpeaking at an impromptu news
OL,16,Fconference at the White House later on
OL,17,FMonday, the president said: "We've
OL,18,Fbeen called this morning by the right
OL,19,Fpeople, the appropriate people, and
OL,20,Fthey want to work a deal."
OL,26,@oD@MOUqD@[O]yD@]OU|D@ZO]
